article.description: — Shamir Bogues scored 21 points and Vermont beat Maine 68-57 on Saturday night.
article.headline: Bogues scores 21 to help Vermont beat Maine 68-57
article.linkText: Bogues scores 21 to help Vermont beat Maine 68-57
article.story: BANGOR, Maine -- — Shamir Bogues scored 21 points and Vermont beat Maine 68-57 on Saturday night. Bogues added seven rebounds for the Catamounts (21-6, 11-1 America East Conference). Ileri Ayo-Faleye had 14 points and Nick Fiorillo hit two 3-pointers and scored 12. Kellen Tynes led the Black Bears (11-15, 3-8) with 17 points and six rebounds. Jaden Clayton added 13 points and four assists. Quion Burns scored nine. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
